      "description": "Federal Reserve Signals Continued Hawkish Stance on Interest Rates",
      "details": "Minutes from the Federal Reserve's latest meeting indicated a strong likelihood of continued interest rate hikes to combat persistent inflation. This signals a prolonged period of tighter monetary policy, which typically increases borrowing costs for consumers and businesses. Higher interest rates can dampen consumer spending by making credit more expensive and encouraging saving over spending, potentially impacting impulse purchases and gifting.",
