      "details": "Tech Giant 'Innovate Solutions' announced it would be laying off 5,000 employees, citing economic headwinds and a need to restructure. This news, widely reported across major outlets, adds to a growing trend of job cuts in the technology sector. Large-scale layoffs can create broader economic anxiety, even among those not directly affected, leading consumers to become more cautious with their spending, particularly on discretionary items and gifts.",
